%  Example parameterfile for L-Gadget2

%  File name parameters:

InitCondFile           /path-to-initial-conditions/ics
OutputDir              /path-to-output-directory

EnergyFile        energy.txt
InfoFile          info.txt
TimingsFile       timings.txt
CpuFile           cpu.txt

RestartFile       restart
SnapshotFileBase  snapshot

% CPU-time limit

TimeLimitCPU      86400
ResubmitOn        0
ResubmitCommand   xyz

CpuTimeBetRestartFile  7200.0


MaxMemSize        6144.0 % maximum allowed memory ceiling per CPU

% Code options

ICFormat              1       % only 1 is presently supported
SnapFormat            1       % only 1 is presently supported


NumFilesWrittenInParallel 1   % maximum number of files for which
                              % simultaneous I/O is done


%  Characteristics of run

TimeBegin           0.02
TimeMax	            1.0

Omega0	              0.3
OmegaLambda           0.7
OmegaBaryon           0.0
HubbleParam           0.7

BoxSize                150.0

Softening             0.020
SofteningMaxPhys      0.020

% Output frequency

OutputListFilename  snapshot_file.txt
OutputListOn        1

TimeBetSnapshot        0
TimeOfFirstSnapshot    0
 
TimeBetStatistics      0.1


% Accuracy of time integration

ErrTolIntAccuracy       0.025

MaxSizeTimestep        0.025 
MinSizeTimestep        0.0008
MaxRMSDisplacementFac  0.25


% Tree algorithm and force accuracy

ErrTolTheta            0.5
TypeOfOpeningCriterion 0
ErrTolForceAcc         0.005


% Parameters that affect memory usage of the code

PartAllocFactor       2.0
TreeAllocFactor       0.7

BufferSize            700  % in MByte

% System of units

UnitLength_in_cm         3.085678e24        ;  1.0 Mpc
UnitMass_in_g            1.989e43           ;  1.0e10 solar masses
UnitVelocity_in_cm_per_s 1e5                ;  1 km/sec
GravityConstantInternal  0





